# Cursor AI Rules for Quizzer Project

## Mandatory Quality Checks

ALWAYS run these checks before committing code:

### Python/Django Backend (/service)
```bash
cd service
black --check --line-length=100 .
flake8 . --max-line-length=100 --extend-ignore=E203,W503
python manage.py test
```

### TypeScript/Svelte Frontend (/app)
```bash
cd app
bun run lint
bun run check
bun run test
bun run build
```

## Project Standards

- Python: Black formatting (100 char lines), Flake8 linting
- TypeScript/Svelte: ESLint + Prettier
- Testing: See app/TESTING.md for philosophy
- CI/CD: GitHub Actions runs these same checks

